i mean i know they used “give the people what they want” in rewind but i’m not surprised cause if you read the description here’s what it says at the very bottom:

All comments featured in Rewind inspired by real comments from the YouTube community.

it makes sense for them to use that especially since dan and phil are really relevant as far as it comes to YouTube and since they weren’t in it youtube felt the need to still use something from them to get views.
